data.description: Welcome home! Step into this spacious 4-bedroom property spanning over 2300 square feet. The heart of the home comes to life as you explore the open-concept living room that seamlessly connects to the kitchen with stainless steel appliances, soft-close cabinets, and granite countertops. Home features a formal dining room, nice size den, and a bonus room that offers endless possibilities. As you step outside, the covered patio and fenced backyard envelops you in tranquility and privacy. Schedule your showing today!
